    tails[idx] = num
```

Otherwise, replace the existing tail with a smaller value. This keeps more options open for future elements while preserving the LIS length.

---

```python
return len(arr) - len(tails)
```

`len(tails)` is the LIS length.

Minimum deletions = `n - LIS`.

